                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6988" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0482</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8199 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“人才为我所有”到“人才为我所用”——HTC公司的灵活用工管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;talent for me&quot; to &quot;talent for my use&quot; —flexible employment management rode of HTC company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王馨，贺晨，赵伟杰，叶丹丹，崔文秀，温婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连海事大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连华泰臣科技服务有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HTC公司；灵活用工；降本增效；管理模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HTC company; flexible employment; cost reduction and efficiency increase; management mode</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">技工人才短缺是制约工业企业发展的重要因素。传统的单一雇佣方式已经无法满足纷繁复杂的市场竞争和用人需求变化，灵活用工成为备受青睐的新型用工方式。HTC公司通过灵活用工摆脱“用工难”问题，在短短几年内迅速崛起，其所采取的灵活用工策略和手段极具探讨价值。是什么原因让企业选择灵活用工？企业又如何利用它来实现降本增效？用工过程中遇到哪些矛盾和挫折？企业又是如何解决的？本案例通过描述HTC公司灵活用工的缘起、灵活用工各阶段产生的问题和矛盾，以及采取的各种管理措施，实现从“人才为我所有”到“人才为我所用”的过程，再现了HTC公司探索建立有效的灵活用工管理模式，实现降本增效，共享双赢的故事。本案例旨在让学员了解灵活用工为企业带来的机遇和挑战，以及有效的灵活用工管理办法。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The shortage of skilled workers is an important factor restricting the development of industrial enterprises. The traditional single employment mode has been unable to meet the complicated market competition and employment demand changes, flexible employment has become a popular new employment mode. &quot;Labor shortage&quot; hinders the development of enterprises. Against this background, HTC company has risen rapidly in just a few years, and its strategy and means to get rid of the labor difficult problem through flexible employment are of great value. What makes companies choose to work flexibly? How can enterprises use it to achieve efficiency reduction? What are the contradictions and setbacks encountered in the employment process? How does the enterprise solve it? This case recreates the story of HTC&#39;s win-win situation with flexible employees by describing the contradictions that arise during the various periods of flexible employment and the various management measures taken to realize the process from &quot;talent for me&quot; to &quot;talent for my use&quot;. This case will allow participants to understand the opportunities and challenges that flexible employment brings to the enterprise, as well as the corresponding flexible employment management methods.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《劳动关系管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">灵活用工含义和类型；混合雇佣理论；灵活用工优势和问题；公平感知社会冲突理论；薪酬激励人岗匹配理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
